        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Construction Success Story</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Real results from our construction implementation expertise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-orange-100 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
